<%= stylesheet_link_tag "privacy_policy/main", media: "all" %>
<div style="background-color: #101010;">
  <%= render partial: "shared/privacy_and_terms/navbar" %>

  <div class="privacy-policy-section">
    <div class="container">
      <%= render partial: "shared/privacy_and_terms/heading", locals: { value: "Privacy Policy" } %>
      <div class="wrapper-text text-white">
        <p>Effective Date: April 17, 2024</p>

        <p>This Privacy Policy explains how ShepyDogs collects, uses, and shares your personal information when you visit or use our services through our website or mobile application.</p>

        <h6>Personal Information We Collect</h6>
        <p>When you interact with our website or app, we automatically collect certain information about your device, including:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Device type</li>
          <li>Browser type</li>
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Operating system</li>
          <li>Time zone</li>
          <li>Cookies</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We refer to this automatically collected information as "Device Information."</p>

        <p>We collect Device Information using technologies like:</p>

        <p>Cookies: Data files placed on your device that often include an anonymous unique identifier. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

        <p>Log Files: These track actions on our site and gather data like your IP address, browser type, and time stamps.</p>

        <p>Web Beacons: Electronic files that monitor how you navigate our site or app.</p>

        <p>Additionally, when you use our services, we may collect information such as:</p>

         <ul>
          <li>Full name</li>
          <li>Address</li>
          <li>Payment information</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We refer to this information as "Order Information."</p>

        <p>With your consent, we may also collect:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Background geolocation</li>
          <li>Physical movement data</li>
          <li>Camera and photo library access</li>
          <li>Authorization data from mobile platforms</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This data is essential for the functionality of our services and will be stored on your device. Once verified, we do not retain this data. You can enable or disable location services through your device settings, but disabling this may impact your ability to earn rewards.</p>

        <h6>How We Use Your Personal Information</h6>
        <p>We use the personal information we collect to:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Provide and maintain our services</li>
          <li>Fulfill transactions</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about updates and offers</li>
          <li>Allow participation in interactive features</li>
          <li>Provide customer support</li>
          <li>Analyze usage to improve our services</li>
          <li>Detect and address technical issues</li>
        </ul>

        <h6>Third-Party Disclosure</h6>
        <p>We do not sell or trade your personal information. We may share information with trusted partners who assist in our operations, as long as they agree to keep it confidential. We may also disclose personal information to comply with legal obligations or to protect our rights and safety.</p>

        <h6>Data Security</h6>
        <p>We prioritize the security of your personal information and employ measures such as:</p>

        <p>Encryption: Sensitive data is encrypted during transmission and storage.</p>
        <p>Access Controls: Limited access to personal data based on necessity.</p>
        <p>Secure Storage: Data is kept in secure environments compliant with industry standards.</p>
        <p>Incident Response: Procedures in place to address potential security breaches promptly.</p>

        <h6>Your Rights</h6>
        <p>You have rights regarding your personal information, including the ability to:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Access your data</li>
          <li>Request corrections</li>
          <li>Object to data sharing</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
        </ul>

        <h6>Data Retention</h6>
        <p>We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, unless a longer retention period is required for legal or compliance reasons.</p>

        <h6>Changes to This Policy</h6>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page. Continued use of our services following any changes signifies your acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

        <h6>Contact Us</h6>
        <p>For inquiries about our privacy practices or to exercise your rights regarding your personal information, please reach out to us through the contact information provided on our website.</p>

        <p>Feel free to customize any sections further to better fit your specific operations or policies!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>